00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:50,320
because there are a few things you should know before you equip this thing. First of all, we're gonna go over, there's probably one or two, maybe three things you should know about this item, but the most important one is this is not a flamethrower for you to charge at somebody in their face.

4
00:00:50,320 --> 00:01:02,320
That's not what this thing is designed for. You're not supposed to just barrel ass into people and light them on fire, because of course, if you take a look at the other flamethrowers, which have a way more cost-efficient compression blast,

5
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:11,319
this thing takes 50 ammo to do it one time, which means you can only do this four times before you're totally out of ammo, so you're not supposed to air blast with this thing.

6
00:01:11,319 --> 00:01:26,689
Only in extreme emergency situations are you supposed to right-click with this thing out, but the other flamethrowers, they're designed to pop people in the air, shoot them with the flare gun, they're designed to knock people around and to charge at people head-on.

7
00:01:26,689 --> 00:01:37,689
Now, of course, you can just charge at people holding the mouse button down with this thing and do a substantial amount of damage. You can do that with all the flamethrowers, but you gotta remember, this thing is not the WM-1 weapon anymore,

8
00:01:37,689 --> 00:01:47,689
because they took away the damage bonus it had. Remember, this thing got brought down to be in line with the stock flamethrower. They brought the stock flamethrower up, and they brought this thing down.

9
00:01:47,689 --> 00:01:58,930
And this thing also, just like the Flogistinator now, never used to have a compression blast. They added that in a patch a couple years ago, so it had a very bad reputation when it first came out.

10
00:01:58,930 --> 00:02:09,099
But I think now, I mean, the guaranteed crits from behind are very powerful still, as you're seeing in this video. It's incredibly powerful, but it has to be used in the right way.

11
00:02:09,099 --> 00:02:22,099
Like I said, you cannot just charge at people anymore. You have to use the backburner as if you were a spy. You have to play Backburner Pyro as if you were a spy with no disguises, because it's pretty much the exact same thing.

12
00:02:22,099 --> 00:02:33,099
