I run straight into a heavy, and he blows me away. That's just how it is. You have to remember to utilize the ambush and the hiding tactics, especially on an open map like Lakeside, or any of the King of the Hill maps, or even on the payload.

15
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:15,800
Backburner Pyro on payload is potentially insane. If you just sit there and hide around a corner where nobody can see you and watch the cart trail in front of you with five dudes on it, you'll kill at least a few of them.

16
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:22,099
